    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="下载"><a href="#下载" class="headerlink" title="下载"></a>下载</h3><p><a href="https://github.com/coreybutler/nvm-windows">nvm-windows官网</a></p><p><a href="https://github.com/coreybutler/nvm-windows/releases">nvm在Github的下载地址</a>,选择exe版本</p><h3 id="常用命令"><a href="#常用命令" class="headerlink" title="常用命令"></a>常用命令</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//查看已安装的node</span><br><span class="line">nvm list </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//安装指定版本的node</span><br><span class="line">nvm install &lt;版本号&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//使用指定版本的node</span><br><span class="line">nvm use &lt;版本号&gt; </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
